n/Fi1r-zIJ6Lh60JhEjWa9zXk4Y0y-\"><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><font color=\"#808080\" size=\"4\">△</font><font color=\"#c0c0c0\"><img src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/4a/mm_thumb.gif\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><font size=\"1\">那啥，预告片凑合着先看看呗</font></font></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fqo7iSDcMwBenwbvxrYzRwALWK1S\"><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">于是！</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>全新第二季·超万能频道</span><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">即将来袭</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">这一次！<span>你的烦恼将如何解决？</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><font color=\"#880000\">--------------------------------------------------我是主播喵的分割线---------------------------------------------</font></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FnlEr1PpMvRgeE5D6lVJxdsxA5Ls\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><font size=\"5\" color=\"#880000\">【烦恼解决游戏】</font></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><font size=\"3\"><span><font color=\"#000000\">&nbsp; </font><font color=\"#ff0000\">&nbsp;</font></span></font><img src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/f4/xklzhuanquan_thumb.gif\"><font color=\"#ff0000\">游戏玩法：</font><font color=\"#000000\">参与者以楼层为单位参与游戏，以接龙的方式说出烦恼，并且解决上一位参与者的烦恼</font><span>&nbsp;。 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><font color=\"#000000\" size=\"3\"><span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1楼由于是第一个发起者，所以只需要说出你的烦恼（沙发福利）</span></font></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><font color=\"#000000\" size=\"3\"><span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2楼则要说出解决1楼烦恼的方法，再继续说出自己的烦恼</span></font></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><font color=\"#880000\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 举个